<p><strong>Saving Throws</strong> Con +9, Wis +6, Cha +6</p>

<p><strong>Skills</strong> Arcana +7, Insight +6, Intimidation +6, Perception +6</p>

<p><strong>Languages</strong> Common, Draconic, Giant</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 9 (5,000 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Keen Smell.</em></strong> Blagothkus has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on smell.</p>

<p><strong><em>Innate Spellcasting.</em></strong> Blagothkus can innately cast the following spells (spell save DC 15), requiring no material components:</p>

<ul>
  <li>3/day each: fog cloud, levitate</li>
</ul>

<p><strong><em>Spellcasting.</em></strong> Blagothkus is a 5th-level spellcaster that uses Intelligence as his spellcasting ability (spell save DC 15, +7 to hit with spell attacks). Blagothkus has the following spells prepared from the wizard spell list:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Cantrips (at will): light, mage hand, prestidigitation</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>1st level (4 slots): detect magic, identify, magic missile, shield</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>2nd level (3 slots): gust of wind, misty step, shatter</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>3rd level (2 slots): fly, lightning bolt</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> Blagothkus attacks twice with his morningstar.</p>

<p><strong><em>Morningstar.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +10 to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. Hit: 21 (3d8 + 8) piercing damage.</p>

